{"tid":2127622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我唔驚中武肺 係驚要隔離","createTime":"2020-07-27T12:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:48:58.000Z","uid":147376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd17da9c68a5530bedb43d62a11a909c838bdac","tid":2127622,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"講真武肺後生死亡率好低 甚至無病徵 <br />\n我驚係驚中咗要俾人隔離 最慘身邊嘅人都因為你而被隔離 連累埋人哋<br />\n隔離有冇嘢做好似坐監咁<br />\n另外又驚會傳到畀老人家 都係一個憂慮"},{"pid":"af1e497192b6497e12bcf761b65cc551c6803d0b","tid":2127622,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"有冇人有同樣嘅諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c352083c70653a648a82c87a35a97513f2ed5576","tid":2127622,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee0f705602f8673e371770d1d4c569e4ac4fec5","tid":2127622,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"例如返工嘅 當有10個同事吖 你中咗10個同事要隔離 同事屋企人都要隔離 坐底都連累四五十個人要隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d030f34aff30f5b44fa4cf8626bb6fe55cc194","tid":2127622,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:11:15.000Z","msg":"你後生身體又冇咩暗病姐<br />\n時間唔同咗就會唔同睇法"},{"pid":"1e000ac4bfd524a45e0096039b2e1391e1ad67ff","tid":2127622,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"知唔知肺炎後遺症有咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604fc2e9ba6e34818ce7e6ed85c2dbff13bd4c4c","tid":2127622,"uid":323228,"lik